Guionista: Jasmin Chong James O'Barr Kyle Wong
Argumento: Based on the hit comic book series "The Crow", a new incarnation where Sergeant Mark Leung and his wife are murdered and their daughter Isabelle taken by a Triad run human trafficking ring. Mark's partner Caitlin races to locate them before the trail runs cold and her chance at rescuing Isabelle disappears into the criminal underworld with them.
One long, uncut shot turned short film, about an 18 year old Australian soldier arriving on the front line of the Turkish battle in World War I, and following his time in battle.
A puzzled college student seeks to assemble an award-winning film from the scattered pieces of his imagination.

Un hospital es asaltado por terroristas. Jason, veterano con estrés postraumático, está allí visitando a un psiquiatra. Su hija, su mujer, un general y otros desconocidos se hallan allí. Jason deberá ponerlos a salvo a todos.

Nombre: Duke of New York in New Ghost City
Argumento: Amid the Covid19 pandemic, a movie producer tricks a director into killing an Asian actor in an attempt to take revenge for the virus. The director gets wind of the plot and decides to go against the producer and set crew.
The hero with a violent past goes to another village and connects with a good soul. He intends to protect Dhanvantari's sacred book, fights the villain, and aims to avenge his sister's death.
Jeff has a crush on a girl that's way outside his social class but he won't let that stop him. He'll do whatever it takes, including breaking a few rules.

La historia de un pequeño grupo de soldados de caballería que son atrapados por el enemigo en un cañón. En el transcurso de unos días, se ven obligados a enfrentar sus diferencias y confiar los instintos de sus enemigos para sobrevivir.
Four ordinary people came from somewhere to harbour to find a work which living for pursuit, things change when they arrive and met someone.
A group of friends decides to document their lives as they search for an underground fight club that exists in the dark web. They put everything on the line for money, respect, and friendship.

Guionista: Abdul Rafay Chandio Fizza Ali Meerza Nabeel Qureshi
Argumento: Quaid-e-Azam Zindabad is a slogan near and dear to many Pakistanis. Nowadays, corruption sweeps across the nation that was once built upon on the basis of being pure and clean. Several institutions are infiltrated through bribery

Argumento: Adaption of the phenomenon-level mobile game "Onmyoji" - film version with the same name that will bring the magnificent oriental fantasy world to life.
